summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department, authorizing construction of Contract No. 6-A of the West Seattle-Alki Sewer Improvement Project to separate the existing combined sewers in the area generally bounded by Southwest Webster Street on the north, 34th Avenue Southwest on the east, Southwest Barton Street and Southwest Roxbury Street on the south, and Puget Sound on the west, and making an appropriation from the Sewer Improvement Fund therefor.
